        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "Requests and Twitch upstream activity for `foam-proxy`. Metrics arrive via OTLP HTTP at the collector, then Prometheus scrapes the collector's Prometheus exporter.",
